{
  "info": {
    "name": "BX Finance — 3-Token Delegated Chain (may_act / RFC 8693)",
    "description": "Tests the full 3-token delegation chain:\n\n1. **Subject Token** (Step 1) — Authorization Code + PKCE. Postman's built-in OAuth2 handler manages the PKCE code generation and callback capture. Click Send; Postman opens its embedded browser for login. After you log in, Postman captures the callback, exchanges the code, and issues the Bearer token automatically. The test script saves it to `subject_token`.\n2. **MCP Token** (Step 2) — RFC 8693 Token Exchange #1. Banking App exchanges the Subject Token for an MCP-scoped token.\n3. **PingOne API Token** (Step 3) — Client Credentials from BX Finance MCP Service. Used to call the PingOne Management API.\n4. **User Lookup** (Step 4) — GET /users/{sub} using Token 3, proving the full chain works end-to-end.\n\n## Setup\nImport this collection, then set these **Collection Variables** (gear icon -> Edit -> Variables):\n\n| Variable | Where to find it |\n|---|---|\n| `PINGONE_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | PingOne Console -> Environment -> Settings |\n| `PINGONE_REGION` | `com` (US) or `eu` / `ca` / `ap` |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_USER_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance User** app |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance Banking App** |\n| `PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Client Secret of **BX Finance Banking App** |\n| `MCP_CLIENT_ID` | Client ID of **BX Finance MCP Service** |\n| `MCP_CLIENT_SECRET` | Client Secret of **BX Finance MCP Service** |\n\n**Redirect URI prerequisite:** Add `https://oauth.pstmn.io/v1/callback` as a Redirect URI on the BX Finance User app in PingOne before running Step 1.\n\n## Running the chain\nRun steps in order: **1 -> 2 -> 3 -> 4**. All token variables are auto-populated by the test scripts.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_ENVIRONMENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Your PingOne environment UUID"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_REGION",
      "value": "com",
      "description": "com | eu | ca | ap"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_USER_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance User app"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance Banking App"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_CORE_CLIENT_SECRET",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client Secret — BX Finance Banking App"
    },
    {
      "key": "MCP_CLIENT_ID",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client ID — BX Finance MCP Service"
    },
    {
      "key": "MCP_CLIENT_SECRET",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Client Secret — BX Finance MCP Service"
    },
    {
      "key": "ENDUSER_AUDIENCE",
      "value": "https://ai-agent.pingdemo.com",
      "description": "Subject Token audience"
    },
    {
      "key": "MCP_RESOURCE_URI",
      "value": "https://mcp-server.pingdemo.com",
      "description": "MCP Token audience"
    },
    {
      "key": "PINGONE_API_AUDIENCE",
      "value": "https://api.pingone.com",
      "description": "PingOne API Token audience"
    },
    {
      "key": "subject_token",
      "value": "",
      "description": "AUTO — saved by Step 1 test script after Postman completes the PKCE flow"
    },
    {
      "key": "mcp_token",
      "value": "",
      "description": "AUTO — set by Step 2"
    },
    {
      "key": "pingone_api_token",
      "value": "",
      "description": "AUTO — set by Step 3"
    },
